column5: just wondering what the snow is like up in huntsville after that cold snap.... by the looks of it more snow coming anyways..
hey which lake do you want to know about or a certain area huntsville is pretty big.

Spent the weekend on Boshkong and Kushog . Still lots of dangerous spots in the narrows due to the fact that they have had too much snow this winter. Lots of slush on the ice. 4-6 inches of slush with 12-15 inches of snow. Stay on the trails!!!!!
basically in the area of burks falls!! have the snowsqualls tooken over?
